---
title: Lemon Pepper Pork Schnitzel with Caramelised Onion Potato Salad
description: Tonight, we're putting on the schnitz! With zesty lemon pepper in the crumb coating, a deluxe potato salad with caramelised onion and a garden salad with a tangy balsamic dressing, this meal is the best of the best!
